title: Merge branch 'web/modals'
message:
Merge branch 'web/modals'

- Refactoring all modals #477
- Fixed modal overflow problem #449
- Remove all unused styles for modals
- Add new ModalWrapper component which handle and contain all modal windows
- Rewrite all modal stores using ReduceStore from flux
- Add fuzzaldrin filtering to modals with searchable content
- Fixed some translation issues, add some missing string
